{"tid":794142,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"百無聊賴","createTime":"2018-08-26T03:31:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-26T03:31:09.000Z","uid":26637,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2b9f35bb0d89e2478870fe84e12dae0b450fe3a6","tid":794142,"uid":26637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T03:31:09.000Z","msg":"我希望呢度係一個，半夜當你問起蝴蝶，就有人同你講蝴蝶；當你問起屋企想裝修，就有人同你講邊度訂造家私平靚正；當你睇完一本書一套電影，想分享都有人會聽你講野；感情煩惱，工作趣事，旅行見聞，我希望同唔同既人傾下計聽多啲唔同既故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果相處的開心既咪出黎聚下，試多啲唔同既活動同玩意，想滑水又有人陪你滑水，想行山又有人陪你行山，想睇展覽又有人陪你睇展覽，放工想揾人happy hour 又有人想同你啤啤佢，我想認識五湖四海既朋友，想同唔同既人一齊玩，希望你會加入我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n謝絕厹娘娘廣告潛水員，如有發現，斬立決<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n會員貴精不貴多，但求交心、活躍，非誠勿擾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeF3N-P1gm-74znVRooIarKaZNullsKBxM9XtXq9Aj05tjBZA/viewform?usp=pp_url\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSeF3N-P1gm-74znVRooIarKaZNullsKBxM9XtXq9Aj05tjBZA%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dpp_url&d=Ffc2IM8%2B%2BBCfU1b%2BtQePjo9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=a63449f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeF3N-P1gm-74znVRooIarKaZNullsKBxM9XtXq9Aj05tjBZA/viewform?usp=pp_url</a>"}]}